import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { ChainId, Config, DAppProvider, MULTICALL_ADDRESSES } from '@usedapp/core'
import { App } from './App'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import {store} from './store'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'

const COVALENT_API_KEY = "ckey_4aed01d0d6e248a7a4ab27acb8a"

const COVALENT_MAINNET = {
  url: "https://api.covalenthq.com/v1/1/",
  transactionsForAddress: "https://api.covalenthq.com/v1/1/address/INPUT_VARIABLE/transactions_v2/?key=INPUT_VARIABLE"
}

const TRANSACTIONS_FOR_ADDRESS = "https://api.covalenthq.com/v1/1/address//transactions_v2/?key="

const config:Config = {
  readOnlyChainId: ChainId.Mainnet,//ChainId.Mainnet,
  readOnlyUrls: {
    [ChainId.Mainnet]: 'https://mainnet.infura.io/v3/3165a249c65f4198bf57200109b8fadf',
    [ChainId.Hardhat]: 'http://127.0.0.1:8545/'
  },
  // multicallAddresses: MULTICALL_ADDRESSES[ChainId.Mainnet]
}

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Provider store={store}>
    <DAppProvider config={config}>
      <App />
    </DAppProvider>
    </Provider>,
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
